{"tid":694020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網絡熱傳】時空旅行者？大學圖書館發現奇妙字條","createTime":"2018-06-08T03:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T04:38:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4278abdbebc74fad9555451a9bb918586688390c","tid":694020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"主頁, 專題熱話, 潮玩新聞 &mdash; 07/06/2018 at 5:16 pm<br />\nby 爆炸哥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07171625/page13413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07171625%2Fpage13413.jpg&h=5c505a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實成件事要自導自演好容易，不過如果覺得係真又感覺好有趣。話說呢位石松拓人喺Twitter出圖，話喺一間大學嘅圖書館一個冇用嘅圖書證櫃入面搵到張字條，上面寫住：「如果你看到這字條，證明時空旅行是存在的。」日期係2085年4月4日，仲有個電話。之後佢跟個電話傳訊息，問嗰個人係咪時空旅行者，得到嘅回覆係佢唔肯定亦都唔敢否認&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;當然有網民唔信啦，但都引嚟超過20萬RT喎。<br />\n<a href=\"http://gameover.com.hk/?p=404576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F%3Fp%3D404576&d=QuZdVptXGdPlftUvT%2Bye5m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=77fef17e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gameover.com.hk/?p=404576</a>"},{"pid":"6ee3246d8cbddceb121962496c64f1074bbdfa95","tid":694020,"uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"Interstellar<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-bfd994f44ec5db148987ab6010f7150a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-bfd994f44ec5db148987ab6010f7150a&h=c838b4c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be1aebe1c482a8472171f749d5fe17bb673d2cc0","tid":694020,"uid":143241,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T03:27:23.000Z","msg":"如果你哋睇到呢個留言,咁就證明時光上網係傳在嘅<br />\n08/06/2199年"},{"pid":"9285984acbb858df4f56b41ab8a029ab050b5ad9","tid":694020,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be1aebe1c482a8472171f749d5fe17bb673d2c